1.15
log
@Identify domains with AF_* instead of PF_* here
Tweaks to SYNOPSIS and RETURN VALUES
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: shutdown.2,v 1.14 2013/07/17 05:42:11 schwarze Exp $
.\"	$NetBSD: shutdown.2,v 1.5 1995/02/27 12:37:11 cgd Exp $
